description:
This is a 30 minute workout called '30 Min CALISTHENICS FULL BODY WORKOUT | Day 2' from the channel Tom Peto Training.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Follow along with this 30 minute full body Calisthenics workout you can do at home with no equipment. Gain muscle, increase strength and develop flexibility with the Calisthenics exercises included in this routine. This beginner friendly workout has difficulty variations included as well as technique tips throughout.
